Name: Combo Assault (Discharge)
Desc:
[Enchant Force]
Attacks the nearby enemy with a bow, and then shoots an arrow flying through space to attack a wide range of enemies.
Arrows deal damage to enemies in a wider range.

H.Old:
Relic Gauge Cost: 100. Bow attack deals damage to up to 5 enemies at 600% damage 7 times. Damaged enemies are inflicted with 1 stacks of the Ancient Curse Debuff.
Arrows deal damage up to 12 enemies at 650% damage 5 times.
Cooldown: 20 sec.
